<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="Aink217-kilavi"> varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta talaimakaṉ mīṭciyuṇarnta tōḻi yāṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante, who was aware of the hero’s return – who had placed a gap in the marriage and separated, told the heroine, who could not bear [it].   </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink217">
<l>peruvarai vēṅkaip poṉmaru ṇaṟuvī</l>
<l>māṉiṉap peruṅkiḷai mēyalāruṅ</l>
<l>kāṉaka nāṭaṉ varavumivaṇ</l>
<l>mēṉi pacappa tevaṉko laṉṉāy</l>
</lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mother, </l>
<l>why does your body fade,</l>
<l rend="space">[just] as he from the land with a forest, </l>
<l>where a big herd of deer species become full from grazing </l>
<l>on gold-like fragrant blossoms </l>
<l>of the Kino tree on the big mountain </l>
<l>comes here? </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
